Some content is not mine to give.  I am reaching out to the creators, but in the
meantime here are the creators:

"Nyanyanyanyanyanyanya!" (Original Composition)
Composer: daniwell (daniwellP)
Original Upload: https://nicovideo.jp
Official YouTube: https://youtu.be
Website: https://aidn.jp
Used under open educational/fair use guidelines. All rights reserved by the original creator.

"Nyanyanyanyanyanyanya!" (UTAU Momone Momo Cover)
Arrangement & Synthesizer Programming: Momomomo (ももももP)
Original Upload: https://nicovideo.jp
Voicebank Project: http://momonemomo.com
Derived from the original work by daniwell. Used for educational purposes.

"Nyan Cat" (Character & Animation Pixel Art)
Creator: Chris Torres (PRguitarman)
Official Hub: http://nyan.cat
Official Profile: https://x.com
Character and visual design used under educational open-source attribution guidelines.

"Nyan nyan nyanyanyanyan" (Illustration)
Creator: studiomarimo
Original Upload: https://www.deviantart.com/studiomarimo/art/Nyan-nyan-nyanyanyanyan-253160677
Platform Profile: https://www.deviantart.com/studiomarimo
Derivative fan work based on Nyan Cat. Used for open educational purposes.
